paymentProcessor.processPayment(new PaymentData("user@example.com", 150.0));
```

In this example, the `PaymentProcessor` context holds a reference to the `PaymentGateway` strategy interface. Based on user input (e.g., selecting PayPal or Stripe), you swap out one concrete strategy implementation for another.

